data.description: Watch the Navy Pier fireworks from your living room! Rarely available 2 bed/2 bath in River North's Silver Tower. Absolutely breathtaking views of the entire city from the South and East. Open concept living and eating spaces include hardwood floors, granite and stainless steel kitchen with mocha cabinetry and sun shades for the large windows. Enjoy entertaining on the living room balcony that overlooks the heart of Chicago. Master bedroom boasts dual closets and en suite bathroom. Unit has in-unit laundry and a separate storage unit in the building. Monthly HOA fee includes HBO, ShowTime and Internet. Amenities include state-of-the-art roof deck with gas grills and lounge furniture, fitness center, and 24-hour door staff. Close to multiple L/subway stations with easy highway access. Walk to restaurants, bars and grocery stores. Deeded garage parking spot additional 35K.
